## Branching Strategy
- **Base branch**: `develop` — all feature/fix PRs target `develop`
- **Production branch**: `main` — only tested code from `develop` is promoted to `main`
- NEVER push directly to `main` or `develop` — always create a PR
- Each agent works in its own git worktree — no shared working directories
- Merge conflicts are resolved at PR time through GitHub

